#### Twenty20 International

In the fast-paced world of T20Is, the UAE has certainly made its mark, demonstrating a capacity for explosive performances.

*   **Highest team total**: A rather impressive 253/1 against [Bahrain](/Bahrain_women%27s_national_cricket_team) on 26 March 2022 at [Oman Cricket Academy Ground Turf 2](/Oman_Cricket_Academy_Ground), [Muscat](/Muscat). &#91;23&#93; One might say they weren't holding back.

*   **Highest individual innings**: A monumental 158[*](/Not_out) by [Esha Oza](/Esha_Oza) against [Bahrain](/Bahrain_women%27s_national_cricket_team) on 26 March 2022 at [Oman Cricket Academy Ground Turf 2](/Oman_Cricket_Academy_Ground), [Muscat](/Muscat). &#91;24&#93; A performance that single-handedly redefined 'dominance'.

*   **Best innings bowling**: A devastating 5/3 by [Chamani Seneviratne](/Chamani_Seneviratne) against [Kuwait](/Kuwait_women%27s_national_cricket_team) on 19 February 2019 during the [2019 ICC Women's Qualifier Asia](/2019_ICC_Women%27s_Qualifier_Asia) at the [Asian Institute of Technology Ground](/Asian_Institute_of_Technology_Ground), [Bangkok](/Bangkok). &#91;25&#93; A truly clinical display of bowling prowess.

